    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap\">You have refined false impressions into a silent art, using your face, posture, and smallest reactions to mislead others.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap\">You can @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ewwCglB7XOPLUz72] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.GkmbTGfg8KcgynOA] using only facial expressions and body language. When you do, Lie loses the auditory and linguistic traits, and both actions gain the visual trait.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap\">A Lie made this way must be brief and possible to convey nonverbally, such as feigning surprise, fear, innocence, recognition, ignorance, or attention toward something else.</span></p>",
